ConsoleGroupcollapsed.summary: The console.groupCollapsed() static method creates a new inline group in the console. Unlike , however, the new group is created collapsed. The user will need to use the disclosure button next to it to expand it, revealing the entries created in the group.

remarks.para: Call to back out to the parent group.
See Using groups in the console in the documentation for details and examples.
